                You'll turn a one-off metric tile into a reusable component with clear props for label, value, trend,
                and status. This is the building block for your subscription, billing, and profile summary tiles later
                in the track.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
                <li>Design a clean stat card layout that works for multiple metrics.</li>
                <li>Pass data into the card using parameters instead of hard-coding values.</li>
                <li>Use subtle badges and colors to communicate status at a glance.</li>
                <li>Prepare the card so you can reuse it in the final <code class="text-[11px]">/admin/dashboard</code>.
                </li>
            </ul>

            <div class="mt-2 pt-3 border-t border-blue-200">
