                        Admin Dashboard Layout</a>
                    <a href="/tips#reusable-stat-cards"
                        class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full text-[11px] sm:text-xs font-medium hover:bg-blue-200 transition-colors">Reusable
